	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratia et pax.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas tuas<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Bullingers Brief, der wohl an <persName ref="person28">Bucer</persName> und <persName ref="person40">Capito</persName> gemeinsam adressiert war, ist nicht erhalten.</note> per <persName ref="person891">Froschouerum</persName> domi accępimus, quo die <placeName ref="place121">Bernam</placeName> iter ingressi sumus, hoc est 5. septembris.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc non est tempus respondendi; eques enim hic tabellarius vester<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Unbekannt.</note> ad iter accinctus est.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">E <placeName ref="place97">Basilęa</placeName> respondebimus et acta <placeName ref="place121">Bernen[sia]</placeName> mittemus<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Siehe unten <ref target="file11094">Nr. 1051</ref>, 2-5 mit Anm. 2f.</note>, quae autoritate et fide senatus et diacosiorum<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">des Kleinen und des Großen Rates.</note> illic conscripta sunt.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="person176">Erasmus</persName><note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6"><persName ref="person176">Ritter</persName>.</note> nobis insciis abiit <placeName ref="place121">Berna</placeName>, etiam si vesperi pridie, quam abiret, eum apud suas edes salutarem.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quo profecto metum iniecit eum restitutum consensum et summam charitatem nondum ex toto corde professum esse, utcunque et coram fratribus et senatu utroque eam <persName ref="person145">Megander</persName> iussu omnium fratrum verbis sane amplissimae consensionis et dilectionis profiteri se testatus sit<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b">sit <hi>am Rande nachgetragen.</hi></note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">A te et caeteris symmystis nostris isthic aliud non petimus, quam ut iudicium differatis, donec acta videritis.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed ipsa vos ęquitas monet alteram aurem nobis servandam esse<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Zur Redensart vgl. Plutarch, Alexander, 42, 2; LB IV 605f.</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Valete in domino.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="person40">Capito</persName> vos salutat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bihelae, 25. septembris.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">M. <persName ref="person28">Bucerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutat te <persName ref="person81">Grynęus</persName> tuus amantissime.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Optimo viro d. Heinricho Bullingero suo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
